    width: 40px;
}
</style>

<h3>Setup</h3>

<ul>
    <li>10 starting cards</li>
    <li>5 / 6 / 7 artifacts</li>
    <li>6 cards in dungeon row, replace dragon attacks</li>
    <li>3 / 2 / 1 / 0 cubes in clank area</li>
    <li>30 clank cubes per player</li>
    <li>Add goblin</li>
</ul>

<h3>Reminders</h3>
<ul>
    <li>take <i>one</i> token when entering a room, not both</li>
    <li>move dragon tracker when taking dragon egg or artifact</li>
    <li>taking an artifact is optional, picking it up is an action (rather than on-enter)</li>
    <li>refill dungeon row only at end of turn</li>
    <li>max 1 dragon attack between turns</li>
    <li>cannot leave dungeon without an artifact</li>
    <li>0 points for dying without an artifact or dying in the depths</li>
    <li>dead players' clank cubes are treated as dragon cubes</li>
    <li>begin countdown track with first player token who leaves the dungeon <i>or</i> is knocked out</li>
    <li>card order is extremely generous, works retrospectively</li>
    <li>"arrive" effects trigger <i>before</i> dragon attacks</li>
    <li>sword for monster path is optional, unless it would kill you</li>
</ul>

<h3>Final Score</h3>
<ul>
    <li>artifacts</li>
    <li>tokens acquired</li>
    <li>points on cards in deck, 1:1</li>
    <li>mastery token for escaping</li>
    <li>tie breaker: most valuable artifact</li>
</ul>

