<h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Mummy's Curse</h3>
<div class="table table-100">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>Mummy begins on llama symbol</li>
                <li>add mummy next to goblin</li>
                <li>include pyramid die</li>
                <li>add supreme monkey idol</li>
                <li>add ankh tokens</li>
                <li>use curse tokens</li>
                <li>add the 40 mummy's curse cards</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <ul>
                <li>curses are not limited</li>
                <li>can only fight mummy if you are in his zone</li>
                <li>after defeating mummy, roll die to determine its new location</li>
                <li>no curses are given if the mummy does not move</li>
                <li>some new items trigger mummy die roll</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<br /><br /><br /><br />
<br />

<h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Gold and Silk</h3>
<div class="table table-row">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Dwarven Mine</h4>
            <p>add 3 mining bonus tokens <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/miningbonus.png" class="artifact" style="vertical-align: middle" /></p>

            <ul>
                <li>mining awards to 1st-2nd-3rd most veins mined</li>
                <li>break ties with depth</li>
                <li>must score points and mine at least once for award</li>
                <li>elevators: pay $1 to use</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Spider Queen's Lair</h4>
            <p>replace 7-point artifact with <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/spiderartifact.png" class="artifact" style="vertical-align: middle" /></p>
            
            <ul>
                <li>shuffle and distribute web tokens face down</li>
                <li>move through web token: spend <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/sword.png" class="icon" /> or extra <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/boot.png" class="icon" />, and claim token</li>
                <li>webbed room: after entering, spend <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/sword.png" class="icon" /> to claim item</li>
                <li>Queen's Web Cache: spend <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/8skill.png" class="icon" />, place a cube to claim a reward</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<br /><br /><br />

<h3 style="margin-bottom: 0;">Temple of the Ape Lords</h3>
<p>replace 30-point artifact with <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/apeartifact.png" class="artifact" style="vertical-align: middle" /></p>

<div class="table table-row">
    <div class="table-row">
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Welcome to the Jungle</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>add 3 unique ape tokens to bronze guardian</li>
                    <li>randomly place remaining 15 ape tokens</li>
                    <li>pick up ape token only when using <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/boot.png" class="icon" />, not teleport</li>
                    <li>take a token for fighting bronze guardian</li>
                    <li>end game: score points for each ape token category</li>
                </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="table-cell tc-6">
            <h4>Monkeying Around the Temple</h4>
            <p>Rage token <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/rng.png" class="artifact" style="vertical-align: middle" /></p>

            <ul>
                <li>shuffle and add gear tokens</li>
                <li>ape tokens
                    <ul>
                        <li>randomly deal 3 to each player</li>
                        <li>discard to rotate adjacent matching gear in any orientation</li>
                        <li>leftovers are not worth points</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>Rage tokens
                    <ul>
                        <li>randomly place <i>face down</i> on marked spaces</li>
                        <li>remaining 4 on space above rage track</li>
                        <li>trigger each when boss marker moves to its space</li>
                        <li>final 4 are triggered when boss <i>would</i> move again</li>
                        <li>rotate all matching gears clockwise, one click</li>
                        <li>discard each after resolving</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>split paths
                    <ul>
                        <li>may choose path in one direction</li>
                        <li>converge in other (cannot turn around)</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<h4>Mini-Campaign</h4>
<p>Campaign token <img src="~/lib/Images/Clank/campaign.png" class="artifact" style="vertical-align: middle" /></p>
<ul>
    <li>play jungle then temple</li>
    <li>jungle
        <ul>
            <li>award campaign tokens to 1st-2nd-3rd</li>
            <li>no token if scoring 0 points</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
    <li>temple
        <ul>
            <li>keep campaign token from jungle round</li>
            <li>keep ape tokens from jungle round instead of receiving 3 at random</li>
            <li>score normally but add campaign token values</li>
            <li>leftover ape tokens score no points</li>
        </ul>
    </li>
</ul>
